    <div id="collapse2" class="collapse tf-panel-collapse-body">
        <p>On the DigiKrimDok portal, the FID Criminology provides retrospectively digitized, older, and mostly out-of-print individual works, series, and journals of high scientific or scientific-historical relevance for free use. Currently, we are digitizing specific suitable works upon request.</p>
