    <div id="collapse3" class="collapse tf-panel-collapse-body">
      <p>The <a href="https://publikationen.uni-tuebingen.de/xmlui/handle/10900/56358">criminological repository</a> contains a collection of online publications that are of great importance to criminological research. Unfortunately, these publications are often scattered across the internet and are only accessible with difficulty. They belong to the realm of "grey literature" and include reports from various ministries, research institutions, and other organizations, as well as crime statistics from different regions, evaluations from the practical and policy sectors, and similar materials. If you or your institution possess such documents that have not yet been included in our repository, we welcome any information or suggestions at <a href="mailto:fidkrim@ifk.uni-tuebingen.de">fidkrim@ifk.uni-tuebingen.de</a>.</p>
